  <summary date="2021-08-13T18:53:06Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Give Our Athletes Level Salaries Act or the GOALS Act

This bill prohibits the use of funds for the 2026 World Cup until the U.S. Soccer Federation agrees to provide equitable pay to the members of the U.S. Women's National Team and the U.S. Men's National Team.</summary>
